{"tid":2164323,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"要今日咁多處女post ，我又開下先","createTime":"2020-08-19T06:47:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-19T06:51:22.000Z","uid":199128,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"55ac069f08e7d2a8561dd71b981929e4d02253d4","tid":2164323,"uid":199128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T06:47:46.000Z","msg":"發唔發覺非處女 或者 女友/老婆係非處既人 好似做保險 或者 信教人士，都係不斷自我加強自己既信念，宣揚非處既好處 ，就好似保險人話保險好，教徒話神好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n即係因為已經係非處一分子，無得講相反野，唯有自己呃自己，就好似如果保險人話保險唔好，信徒話神唔好，先至係新聞。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咩身份既人講咩身份既野，但唔想自卑 or 唔想冇人要 or俾社會歧視，就只可以講對自己有利既野<br />\n<br />\n利申：保險，宗教只是例子，冇煲貶。婚姻角度，非處好過處就真係想唔通。"},{"pid":"4411ea1d284ec860ca6339c95f164b65cea6df33","tid":2164323,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T06:50:15.000Z","msg":"破條女處真係好爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n欣賞個處女膜<br />\n再欲拒還迎咁比你抽插<br />\n感受下兩邊闣包住你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad3e89a91db99a1ea5e306ee7271519118ad8f40","tid":2164323,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T06:51:22.000Z","msg":"我淨係知道有一班人<br />\n<br />\n個頭屌對家去人化嗌手足做曱甴<br />\n<br />\n呢頭自己嗌手足做肉便器做公廁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">屌佢老母玩撚夠未？少少尊重都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-small\"><span class=\"violet\">btw, 佢班人mark左係可疑ac黎, 平時好多都係開垃圾post多(e.g. <a href=\"https://na.cx/i/8EMYLSp.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8EMYLSp.png&d=MYvC0VRZm9a3oqKPvUvInFYPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=eb0c23e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/8EMYLSp.png</a>), 大家